Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0110,,Apollon, do you remember the day the world began?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to a miracle, the sacred and formless void
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was filled with over a billion galaxies, each with over a billion stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The miracle of our meeting above this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we begin to walk a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Skies of Aquaria{\i0} again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir! I'll clean up right—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only reason it keeps getting shown, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else cares about it one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget how lovely you smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like so much about this movie, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you fancy Alisia, the girl who played Silvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just watch as destiny flies off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see her, that's all I can think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over loading the films.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a break, Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just clean up the seats before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Even if I have to wait for 12,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, there's still trash down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'll leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fan... of {\i1}Skies of Aquaria{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. This is the first time I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please, um, tell me your name? Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mikono Suzushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Amata! Amata Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you sell posters for this movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's over ten years old. They don't make them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, would you mind talking to me for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear more about {\i1}Skies of Aquaria{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to finish up some work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to wait for 12,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! No! Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind waiting just outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be out in five, no, three minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three in each should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a cute girl to boot. I must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't go! Don't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could only watch as destiny flew away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak out, Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to wait for 12,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this song was composed, I'm sure no one even imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the Aquarias would have to go into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Abductors came through the Dimension Gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've destroyed our cities and taken away our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know why they do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, we know nothing about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we, the Daughters of Heaven, work together, we—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Miss Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have deployed four times and \Nexperienced Union in an Aquaria, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell your fellow Daughters about the rapture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of being chosen by the holy guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Offering your purity to an Aquaria is pure—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure Union with boys is so much more intense than doing it with girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impure thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, the Guize Stone protects the purity of the Daughters of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impure Unions are completely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Aquaria is a sacred cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot brook a woman who has been sullied by a man's touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us on, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}New China City's traffic core was paralyzed in an Abductor attack. Repairs are underway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Abductors attacked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Abductors are making this place too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theater's customers are drying up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could come out anywhere at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Aquarias fight them off, but they just keep on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abductors or not, I can't stand being cooped up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get some sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some optimistic thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people call it stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my cat, Shush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he likes being around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of a weird-looking cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him running from the Abductors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, tell me about the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Skies of Aquaria{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's based on a book about a war with the Dark Angels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that supposedly took place a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That children's story about what \Nhappened 12,000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the movie didn't do that well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the theme song won awards at film festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I love that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The singer was the girl who played Silvie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Alisia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a great actress, she seemed really nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so pretty it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! Shush, don't eat the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you got, maggots?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't fit to lick my boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't pilot an Aquaria if you don't have guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me, you worms? Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the slack or I'll taze your worthless asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to miss, Cayenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just slipped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you having another vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wedding in mourning clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mourning clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! If I had girls cheering for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be much more motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only the Berlin wasn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy! You're not thinking of sneaking to the other side again, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, Commander Donar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna need something a little stronger than a taze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! You're already doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I thought I could get into Neo-Deava and score Unions with all the hot chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so close, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even seen one yet, let alone talked to one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a complete disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know, Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, somewhere, there's a school that trains Elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people who pilot the Aquarias.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only people who've been chosen by the Aquarias and granted special powers can go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like Apollon and Silvie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, have you ever wanted to pilot an Aquaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd never be chosen by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a useless pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead! I'll catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Respond, Kagura. Stop fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Mithra Gnis is just a test model.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The objective of this mission is strictly information gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be Vega.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, nine, ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Useless pair," she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depressing words, but when she says them so cheerfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long ya gonna be in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, I can't hold it om anymore! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be out right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abductors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! To the shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Aquaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Abductors just don't know when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time we chase 'em off, they come back with more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the chitchat, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll intercept them with the Aquaria Type-M!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the legend guide our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've certainly brought quite a party with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's heavy damage at ground zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Principal, I mean Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think those boys out there have terrible discipline?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Discipline? As if you could claim your girls are any better!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large Abductor unit is approaching the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no data on it! We've never seen it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never seen that machine before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing's on a different level from the other Abductors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stronger and faster than anything we've faced!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're reading vital signs from inside the enemy machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's piloted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A being from another dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fighting in circles around the Aquaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that Abductor's playing with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vectors are taking heavy damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachyon levels falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Principal! I mean, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're authorized to deploy the Type-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have the Type-M and \Nthe Type-F operating at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! You know this is forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let the Type-M be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get that Type-F out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target acquired!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missiles, locked on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Type-F?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet at last, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are so rough when they fight. It just looks disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne! It's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can only pray that the worst does not come to pass:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boys and girls together in Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how close they get, they are doomed to never touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier of chastity, the Guize Stones will see to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't that funny. The new prey smells different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch him in a pincer attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Don't screw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold still already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid boys! Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they even trying to cooperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us down, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mikono?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my body... it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather my body get hurt... than my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Type-M, do you read? Come back us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening! Malloy's taken serious damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His machine's out of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic! You boys can't even—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on all fours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! Stop! You're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their aura levels are dropping sharply!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Unions are breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:21:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Aquarias!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold back any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.65,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix! Sazanka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Who told you to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno! I got pulled back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Aquarias ejected the Elements on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mikono.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata? Sorry for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wings of the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vital signs from inside Vector Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone snuck in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a terrorist hijack the Vector?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a boy and a girl? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.21,0:23:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly! Eject them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:24:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! Their life energy has merged with the Vector's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if those two were called by...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.20,0:24:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.65,0:24:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a Vector cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like I know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.77,0:24:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.32,0:24:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.62,0:24:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.21,0:24:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shatter the name of falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as it shatters, speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.45,0:24:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak the name of truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.92,0:24:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, you will inherit a new legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.25,0:24:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.90,0:24:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have to speak the name of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.10,0:25:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genesis Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.69,0:25:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GO! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.36,0:25:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.81,0:25:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.30,0:25:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.97,0:25:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion. He knows the forbidden name...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.96,0:25:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop! This Union...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.87,0:25:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, what is Aquarion? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.07,0:25:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! They have the Guize Stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.98,0:25:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't complete the forbidden Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.76,0:25:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.49,0:25:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, our rules and our feelings will be torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:26:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be torn apart... and then burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.29,0:26:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to burst! Something in me is going to burst...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.64,0:26:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.30,0:26:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion is... evolving!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.55,0:26:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.72,0:26:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells... awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.85,0:26:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The forbidden name, engraved now unto a new body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.95,0:27:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of the end... is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.20,0:27:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0110,,Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.75,0:27:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0110,,My brain is boiling over...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.12,0:27:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0110,,It's pumping through my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.66,0:27:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0110,,Now I know what that smell was...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.55,0:27:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.62,0:27:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion, the forbidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.78,0:27:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's using Vector Z as the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew the Aquarias had another form?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.25,0:27:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said impure Unions couldn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.94,0:27:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.40,0:27:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.43,0:27:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.10,0:27:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "Evol" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.10,0:27:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.47,0:27:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.35,0:27:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.71,0:27:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.38,0:27:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.15,0:27:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist who hijacked an Aquaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.80,0:28:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrorist?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.63,0:28:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.71,0:28:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata isn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.49,0:28:03.99,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.58,0:28:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? A couple of civilians are the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.99,0:28:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! Override the Union from headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.75,0:28:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.34,0:28:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Status?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.78,0:28:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! It just won't respond to our commands!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.40,0:28:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.80,0:28:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.57,0:28:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Principal! I mean, Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.78,0:28:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Aquarion?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.61,0:28:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We purposely separated the boys from the girls into Aquaria Type-M and Type-F.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.14,0:28:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now male and female are together as one; a complete being.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.67,0:28:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can a mortal use the weapon of a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.44,0:28:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.82,0:28:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get up and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.93,0:29:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.93,0:29:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.49,0:29:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.35,0:29:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here! We can't fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.70,0:29:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out! You can get us out of here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.99,0:29:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.86,0:29:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata! We have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.29,0:29:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a useless pair like us do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.87,0:29:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.45,0:29:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.83,0:29:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.16,0:29:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not little ones either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.47,0:29:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three large units confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.30,0:29:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.79,0:29:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kagura, we have official orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return to Altair with us immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that geezer Izumo send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.34,0:30:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already found Rare Iguras.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.86,0:30:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Further combat would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.41,0:30:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combat isn't meaningless until I say it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.75,0:30:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.55,0:30:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough sitting around!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.50,0:30:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.03,0:30:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, unlock the lever, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.73,0:30:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.65,0:30:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica's Element power was channeled through the machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.61,0:30:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her power is resonating with the boy's!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.67,0:30:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a mixed Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.99,0:30:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, the Aquaria has powers we've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.16,0:31:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.96,0:31:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.74,0:31:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're holding me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.43,0:31:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.85,0:31:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not using this, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.51,0:31:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.05,0:31:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.28,0:31:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.94,0:31:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna stick my fangs into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.92,0:31:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stole a part from another machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.75,0:31:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's moving like an animal... or a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.14,0:31:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.65,0:31:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.05,0:31:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... no... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.89,0:31:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.79,0:31:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's done nothing but whine this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.75,0:31:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle! Suck it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.80,0:32:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono's just a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.89,0:32:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I even protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.20,0:32:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a funeral procession?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.62,0:32:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding in mourning clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.80,0:32:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dark vision I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.27,0:32:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his Element power, the prophecy of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.01,0:32:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He foresees terrible things that will happen to those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.68,0:32:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come we can see his vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.02,0:32:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Aquarion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.07,0:32:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has reclaimed its terrible, forbidden name,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.66,0:32:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is showing us the prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.65,0:32:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the disaster foretold in the prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.10,0:32:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terrible Union of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:32:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.36,0:32:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.69,0:33:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy? Show us your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.94,0:33:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.08,0:33:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.52,0:33:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.68,0:33:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smelly wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.14,0:33:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.45,0:33:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.29,0:33:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fault, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.97,0:34:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caused this worthless Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.77,0:34:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged Mikono in with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.75,0:34:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire disaster is your damn fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.38,0:34:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.31,0:34:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.10,0:34:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I get excited, I fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.99,0:34:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has happened ever since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.15,0:34:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else hates me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.66,0:34:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It even took her away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.21,0:34:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to use my power again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.55,0:34:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanted to protect Mikono, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.51,0:34:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.89,0:34:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just put her into even more danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.81,0:34:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have known that I can't protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.81,0:34:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.24,0:34:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.03,0:35:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, you smelly wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.78,0:35:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shields falling! Aquarion's not going to last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.94,0:35:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To inherit a legend is to become a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.59,0:35:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared to do that, Amata Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.77,0:35:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.47,0:35:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called us a useless pair, and said that you're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.77,0:35:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're amazing, Amata.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.39,0:35:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've only just met, but you're willing to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.28,0:35:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm weak, and all I ever do is cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.95,0:35:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.83,0:35:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.68,0:35:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.95,0:35:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.27,0:36:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.32,0:36:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's small...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.73,0:36:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.26,0:36:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.10,0:36:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.57,0:36:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.33,0:36:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion is... flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.79,0:36:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That acceleration isn't all coming from Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're almost into orbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.18,0:36:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be that boy's Element Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.21,0:37:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.26,0:37:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.69,0:37:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.32,0:37:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dimension Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.65,0:37:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.90,0:37:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but you're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.82,0:37:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo! But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.70,0:37:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Can still fight"? This is no time for jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.33,0:37:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just admit you've lost and come back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.63,0:37:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.09,0:38:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.93,0:38:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.09,0:38:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.94,0:38:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.55,0:38:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not nearly good enough for Mikono.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.85,0:38:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne. Zessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.00,0:38:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the boy and girl back to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.89,0:38:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger on the boy, but the girl's useless to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.48,0:39:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just let someone who has been inside Aquarion leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.94,0:39:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.82,0:39:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.03,0:39:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one person who'll wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.48,0:39:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that flying boy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.15,0:39:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.11,0:39:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wild child's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.18,0:40:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.75,0:40:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to my Gnis?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.89,0:40:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how was the harvest?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.16,0:40:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.22,0:40:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My very own wench.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.06,0:41:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unions are supposed to be really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.57,0:41:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's okay if you're not very good the first time.
